Class GridsLinkedList

java.lang.Object
org.example.gui.pojo.GridsLinkedList
public class GridsLinkedList extends Object
As a collection of data, this class passes data between the class Wavelet and the class MyPanel. All data processed by wavelet will be packed and passed to the class MyPanel to display. The data structure is a linkedlist. @Auther Zhilun LI @Date 02.07.2022 @Version Prototype
